scene.message:
Butterfly: I've been waiting.{waitkey}{clearbox}By saving the boy called Toro{nl}
from a Persona's power, the{nl}
Snow Queen's power has waned.{waitkey}{clearbox}The door sealed fast in ice{nl}
should open now.{waitkey}{clearbox}It is the entrance to one of{nl}
the three towers - the{nl}
Tower of Thanatos.{waitkey}{clearbox}This tower is perilous in{nl}
the extreme, brimming with{nl}
demons of immense power.{waitkey}{clearbox}Gathering the "Mirror Shards"{nl}
here will be quite the trial.{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, yes - let me give you{nl}
a warning about the towers.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you set foot in any{nl}
tower, you cannot leave until{nl}
its master falls. Think first.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Welcome.{nl}
This is the entrance to the{nl}
Tower of Thanatos.{waitkey}{clearbox}Of the three masters, Thanatos{nl}
holds the strongest will.{nl}
Steel yourselves.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, for you as you are now,{nl}
such a warning may be{nl}
needless.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you set foot in any{nl}
tower, you cannot leave until{nl}
its master falls. Think first.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Welcome.{nl}
This is the entrance to the{nl}
Tower of Thanatos.{waitkey}{clearbox}This tower is perilous in{nl}
the extreme, brimming with{nl}
demons of immense power.{waitkey}{clearbox}Your odds are slim as you{nl}
are. If you insist on going,{nl}
I won't stop you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you set foot in any{nl}
tower, you cannot leave until{nl}
its master falls. Think first.{waitkey}{ret}

A heavy, cold air drifts{nl}
from beyond the door.{waitkey}{clearbox}The door is frozen solid{nl}
and won't budge.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Bad feeling here.{nl}
The air's heavy, like the{nl}
hospital basement.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yuriko's gone now,{nl}
yet this room still feels{nl}
cold somehow.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm hungry~{nl}
How long does this{nl}
life go on?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The god who governs{nl}
death... Thanatos is the one{nl}
Persona I'd rather not wear.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Whoa~{nl}
cold~ cold~{waitkey}{clearbox}It's colder here than the{nl}
other rooms, seriously.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ah{wait_fr:30}-choooo!!{nl}
Dang it~!{waitkey}I wanna get the school back{nl}
without all this ice, fast.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: "The Tower of Thanatos"?{nl}
Thanatos is the god of the{nl}
underworld. I'd not want him{waitkey}as a friend.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Wanting to stay{nl}
beautiful... I can't say I{nl}
don't understand Yuriko.{waitkey}{ret}
